* PSF generation for Alanine Dipeptide
*

! 1. Read Topology and Parameters
read rtf card name top_all36_prot.rtf
read para card name par_all36m_prot.prm

! 2. Read Sequence from PDB
read sequ pdb name alanine_dipeptide.pdb

! 3. Generate the Segment (The "building" step)
! We use "setup" to build missing atoms (like hydrogens)
generate A setup warn

! 4. Read the coordinates
read coor pdb name alanine_dipeptide.pdb

! 6. Write the output files
write psf card name alanine_dipeptide.psf
write coor pdb name alanine_dipeptide_out.pdb

stop
